column1: Table Title: Air Cargo Tonnage, Monthly
Source: CIVIL AVIATION AUTHORITY OF SINGAPORE
Refers to Changi Airport only.  Data exclude passenger baggage, diplomatic cargo and aircraft stores.  Data provided are based on flight origin/destination.
Total is the sum of Imports and Exports.

Imports is a sum of direct imports and tranship imports.  Direct imports refer to cargo that arrived directly from origin and are offloaded in Singapore.  Tranship imports refer to cargo that arrived and transited via Singapore.

Exports is a sum of direct exports and tranship exports.  Direct exports refer to cargo that are uploaded in Singapore and departed directly to destination.  Transhipment exports refer to cargo that departed after transiting in Singapore.

NotesNumbers may not add up to the totals due to rounding.Data are the latest available at the time of access or download. Some statistics, particularly those for the most recent time periods, are provisional and may be subject to revision at a later date.
